{
    "name": "kdal-lang",
    "displayName": "KDAL Language Support",
    "description": "Full IDE experience for KDAL device headers (.kdh) and driver files (.kdc) - syntax highlighting, lint, compile, simulate, and more.",
    "version": "0.1.0",
    "publisher": "phuctrong552003",
    "license": "GPL-3.0-or-later",
    "icon": "icons/kdal-icon.png",
    "engines": {
        "vscode": "^1.80.0"
    },
    "main": "./out/extension.js",
    "activationEvents": [
        "workspaceContains:**/*.kdh",
        "workspaceContains:**/*.kdc"
    ],
    "categories": [
        "Programming Languages",
        "Snippets",
        "Linters",
        "Other"
    ],
    "keywords": [
        "kdal",
        "kernel",
        "driver",
        "embedded",
        "linux",
        "device-tree",
        "kdc",
        "kdh"
    ],
    "homepage": "https://github.com/NguyenTrongPhuc552003/kdal",
    "bugs": {
        "url": "https://github.com/NguyenTrongPhuc552003/kdal/issues"
    },
    "repository": {
        "type": "git",
        "url": "https://github.com/NguyenTrongPhuc552003/kdal"
    },
    "scripts": {
        "vscode:prepublish": "npm run compile",
        "compile": "tsc -p ./",
        "watch": "tsc -watch -p ./",
        "package": "vsce package"
    },
    "devDependencies": {
        "@types/node": "^18.0.0",
        "@types/vscode": "^1.80.0",
        "typescript": "^5.3.0",
        "@vscode/vsce": "^3.0.0"
    },
    "contributes": {
        "languages": [
            {
                "id": "kdh",
                "aliases": [
                    "KDAL Device Header",
                    "kdh"
                ],
                "extensions": [
                    ".kdh"
                ],
                "configuration": "./language-configuration.json",
                "icon": {
                    "light": "./icons/kdh-file.svg",
                    "dark": "./icons/kdh-file.svg"
                }
            },
            {
                "id": "kdc",
                "aliases": [
                    "KDAL Driver Code",
                    "kdc"
                ],
                "extensions": [
                    ".kdc"
                ],
                "configuration": "./language-configuration.json",
                "icon": {
                    "light": "./icons/kdc-file.svg",
                    "dark": "./icons/kdc-file.svg"
                }
            }
        ],
        "grammars": [
            {
                "language": "kdh",
                "scopeName": "source.kdh",
                "path": "./syntaxes/kdh.tmLanguage.json"
            },
            {
                "language": "kdc",
                "scopeName": "source.kdc",
                "path": "./syntaxes/kdc.tmLanguage.json"
            }
        ],
        "snippets": [
            {
                "language": "kdh",
                "path": "./snippets/kdh.json"
            },
            {
                "language": "kdc",
                "path": "./snippets/kdc.json"
            }
        ],
        "commands": [
            {
                "command": "kdal.compile",
                "title": "KDAL: Compile Driver",
                "icon": "$(play)"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.lint",
                "title": "KDAL: Lint File",
                "icon": "$(checklist)"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.init",
                "title": "KDAL: Create New Project",
                "icon": "$(add)"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.simulate",
                "title": "KDAL: Simulate Device",
                "icon": "$(debug-start)"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.dtgen",
                "title": "KDAL: Generate Device Tree"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.testgen",
                "title": "KDAL: Generate Test"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.showToolchainInfo",
                "title": "KDAL: Show Toolchain Info"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.installSDK",
                "title": "KDAL: Install SDK"
            },
            {
                "command": "kdal.redetectToolchain",
                "title": "KDAL: Re-detect Toolchain"
            }
        ],
        "menus": {
            "editor/title": [
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdc",
                    "command": "kdal.compile",
                    "group": "navigation"
                },
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdh || resourceLangId == kdc",
                    "command": "kdal.lint",
                    "group": "navigation"
                }
            ],
            "editor/context": [
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdc",
                    "command": "kdal.compile",
                    "group": "kdal@1"
                },
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdh || resourceLangId == kdc",
                    "command": "kdal.lint",
                    "group": "kdal@2"
                },
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdh",
                    "command": "kdal.simulate",
                    "group": "kdal@3"
                },
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdh",
                    "command": "kdal.dtgen",
                    "group": "kdal@4"
                },
                {
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdc",
                    "command": "kdal.testgen",
                    "group": "kdal@5"
                }
            ],
            "commandPalette": [
                {
                    "command": "kdal.compile",
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdc"
                },
                {
                    "command": "kdal.simulate",
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdh"
                },
                {
                    "command": "kdal.dtgen",
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdh"
                },
                {
                    "command": "kdal.testgen",
                    "when": "resourceLangId == kdc"
                }
            ]
        },
        "taskDefinitions": [
            {
                "type": "kdal",
                "required": [
                    "command"
                ],
                "properties": {
                    "command": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "The kdality subcommand to run (compile, lint, simulate, dt-gen, test-gen)"
                    },
                    "file": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Target .kdh or .kdc file"
                    }
                }
            }
        ],
        "configuration": {
            "title": "KDAL",
            "properties": {
                "kdal.toolchainPath": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "default": "",
                    "description": "Path to directory containing kdalc and kdality binaries. Leave empty to auto-detect from KDAL_HOME or PATH."
                },
                "kdal.stdlibPath": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "default": "",
                    "description": "Path to KDAL standard library (.kdh files). Auto-detected if empty."
                },
                "kdal.lintOnSave": {
                    "type": "boolean",
                    "default": true,
                    "description": "Automatically lint .kdh and .kdc files on save."
                }
            }
        },
        "walkthroughs": [
            {
                "id": "kdal.getStarted",
                "title": "Get Started with KDAL",
                "description": "Write your first Linux kernel driver in two steps.",
                "steps": [
                    {
                        "id": "installSDK",
                        "title": "Install the KDAL SDK",
                        "description": "Run **KDAL: Install SDK** from the Command Palette, or use the one-liner:\n\n```\ncurl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/NguyenTrongPhuc552003/kdal/main/scripts/installer/install.sh | sh\n```\n\nOr [build from source](https://github.com/NguyenTrongPhuc552003/kdal/blob/main/docs/installation.md).",
                        "media": {
                            "markdown": ""
                        },
                        "completionEvents": [
                            "onCommand:kdal.installSDK"
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "createProject",
                        "title": "Create Your First Project",
                        "description": "Open the Command Palette and run **KDAL: Create New Project** to scaffold a driver project.",
                        "media": {
                            "markdown": ""
                        },
                        "completionEvents": [
                            "onCommand:kdal.init"
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "writeDriver",
                        "title": "Write Your Driver",
                        "description": "Open the generated `.kdc` file and start writing event handlers. Use snippets like `onprobe`, `onread`, `onwrite` for fast scaffolding.",
                        "media": {
                            "markdown": ""
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "compileAndSimulate",
                        "title": "Compile & Simulate",
                        "description": "Click the **Play** button in the editor title bar to compile, or use **KDAL: Simulate Device** to dry-run your driver without a kernel.",
                        "media": {
                            "markdown": ""
                        },
                        "completionEvents": [
                            "onCommand:kdal.compile"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
}